Introducing Parity 🚀 Rocket

Show an optimal discount based on each visitor's local buying power

Parity Rocket determines each visitor’s location and buying power, then offers them the perfect discount. This means visitors from poorer countries can now afford your products because they see bigger discounts, while visitors from richer countries don’t see a discount at all and pay your regular prices.

If you want to increase conversion rates

Run a special holiday deal every day of the year

There’s nothing more powerful than a perfectly timed holiday deal. With Parity Rocket, your site will feature a relevant conversion-boosting holiday promotion every single day of the year.

More than 50 popular holidays come built-in and can be easily customized. When combined with location-based pricing, these holiday deals create a powerful and reliable conversion booster.

Discover unique and powerful Parity Rocket features

Why else will Parity 🚀 Rocket boost your conversion rates?

VPN Protection

Parity Rocket includes VPN, proxy server and Tor network detection to ensure accurate location-based pricing, even if your visitors try to mask their true location. 

Target Regions in United States, India, and China

Easily break down the United States, India, and China into multiple distinct economic tiers. For example, your visitors from New York and Detroit can see different discounts. This lets you increase conversion rates even if you’re targeting a single market, like the US.

Urgency-Boosting Countdown Timer

With a single click, you can add a real-time countdown timer to your banner. It instantly creates a sense of urgency and encourages quicker decision-making which will significantly boost your conversion rates.

Attention-Grabbing Animations

Subtle animations help your banner stand out, so more visitors see the offer, apply the discount, and complete their purchase.

Display Offer Details Anywhere on Your Website

You can show the full Parity banner message or just parts of it anywhere on your website. Highlight the visitor’s country, flag, discount, or reason for the deal exactly where it matters most so they never miss their localized offer.

Sticky Banner for Maximum Visibility

The banner can remain fixed on the page, ensuring visitors always see your affordable offer no matter where they navigate.

Exit-Intent Popups

Trigger location-based, last-minute discount popups to win back visitors who are about to leave without purchasing. These popups have been professionally designed for you. Simply toggle a switch to turn on this proven conversion booster.

Seamless Integration Across Platforms

Easily integrate Parity Rocket into any website or platform that supports JavaScript tag insertion. This includes WordPress, WooCommerce, Shopify, Webflow, ClickFunnels, and virtually all other platforms.

    Frequently asked questions:

    • 1. How does Parity Rocket adjust discounts for different locations?

      Parity Rocket uses geo-location technology to determine each visitor’s country and their local purchasing power. Based on pre-defined economic parity groups of countries, it then either picks an optimal discount or keeps the original full price, ensuring that your pricing performs well globally. The discounts are easy to set-up and you always remain in full control of your pricing.
